Nana Bryant https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nana_Bryant 0 Nana Bryant (November 23, 1888 – December 24, 1955) was an American film, stage, and television actress. She appeared in more than 100 films between 1935 and 1955. She was born in Lancaster, Ohio, and died in Hollywood, California.
